_sText:
Ar_anubis_strip is a trimmed version of de_anubis map from Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game. 

De_anubis map cannot be ported in full size, so it had to be cut to the optimal size. 

De_anubis - 2019's Mapcore Mapping Contest Winner!

https://www.mapcore.org/topic/24083-csgo-exotic-places-contest-top-4-winners/

Complete the task: 

A bomb defusal map, installed in the City.
